Endurance					KEY:Animal Companion Feat ~ Endurance						CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:AnimalCompanionFeat																																											DESC:You gain a +4 bonus on the following checks and saves: Swim checks made to resist nonlethal damage from exhaustion; Constitution checks made to continue running; Constitution checks made to avoid nonlethal damage from a forced march; Constitution checks made to hold your breath; Constitution checks made to avoid nonlethal damage from starvation or thirst; Fortitude saves made to avoid nonlethal damage from hot or cold environments; and Fortitude saves made to resist damage from suffocation. You may sleep in light or medium armor without becoming fatigued.																																																																				ABILITY:FEAT|AUTOMATIC|Endurance																		SOURCEPAGE:p.112
